snippet.title: PAYDAY 2: Ukrainian Prisoner Heist Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
PAYDAY 2: Ukrainian Prisoner Heist and the Guardians Tailor Pack are now available on Steam! Vlad has been taken prisoner by the Golden Dagger Triad! Thanks to Jiu Feng's intel, the PAYDAY gang know he’s being held in the San Francisco docks. You know what to do next, heisters - but before you head out, make sure to check out the new outfits!

Buy the Ukrainian Prisoner Heist: https://ovk.af/UkrainianPrisonerYS
Buy the Guardians Tailor Pack: https://ovk.af/UkrainianPrisonerYS2
